Subject: Dictated Concept Refinement Fabric Source

Description: Preserved source note for a Stack-Overflow-like concept refinement platform where conversation explanations can become refined root nodes by community attention.

& [DictatedConceptRefinementFabricSource] is the preserved user direction
  + [source_status] is preserved_raw_direction
  + [captured_request] is part of the social fabric should raise attention by anchoring meaning around nodes in a system like Stack Overflow coordinates user contributed concepts and lets users rate concepts
  + [extended_request] is take the pattern further so one explanation in a conversation can replace the root node in the conversation by upvote and become a concept refinement platform
  + [attention_shape] is community-contributed explanations orbiting a concept root with vote, trust, evidence, and lineage signals
  + [root_replacement_shape] is a promoted explanation becomes the current concept root for a scope while prior roots remain preserved as lineage and dissent context
  + [preservation_boundary] is source direction only, not canonical specification authority until separately processed
  + [outside] is proof of truth by upvote, erased lineage, centralized compulsory canon, private capture, reputation farming, and implementation before gates

  = must: preserve upvote as an attention signal, not truth
  = must: preserve the root replacement idea without erasing previous roots or dissent
  = must: keep implementation outside until platform, consent, moderation, and abuse gates exist
